 mixed region due to the Fickian diffusion. The difference between diffusion rate and crystallization induces crystallization front instabilities, and a characteristic length δ=vd/vc\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
